      "description": "Ready for a rewarding challenge? This vehicle is the ultimate diamond in the rough for a dedicated mechanic or restoration specialist! While it currently requires significant mechanical repairs and a full cosmetic overhaul to return to its former glory, it offers a solid foundation for someone with the skills to bring it back to life. It's an affordable entry point for a ground-up project that you can truly make your own!",
