    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for experienced mechanics or those looking for a dedicated project car. The engine currently does not start and will require a full rebuild or replacement to be roadworthy again. Externally, there is significant rust on the quarter panels and several deep dents along the passenger side. The interior shows heavy wear, with torn upholstery and a non-functional dashboard cluster. It is being sold strictly as-is, and the buyer will need to arrange for a tow.",
